<plot>Every May, hundreds of motorcyclists depart Ontario, California for a ten day ride across the heartland of America to bring attention to America's POW/MIA issue. The veterans are joined by family. friends and other veterans as they make their was to Washington, DC for a memorial at The Wall and a rally with thousands of motorcyclists at the Pentagon.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?341009</url></doc>
